                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-content">
                    <p>Bought this for my wife's anniversary gift. She loved it! The colors are vibrant and the craftsmanship is outstanding. The only minor issue was that it took a little longer to arrive than expected, but well worth the wait.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Related Products -->
        <div class="related-products">
            <h2 class="section-title">You May Also Like</h2>
            <div class="products-grid">
